quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  20,99,"This is how We relate to you [O Prophet] from the stories of the past, and We have given you a Reminder<sup>33</sup> from Us.","[33] i.e., the Qur’an."
  20,100,"Whoever turns away from it will bear a heavy burden on the Day of Resurrection,",""
  20,101,"abiding therein forever<sup>34</sup>. What a terrible burden they will carry on the Day of Resurrection!","[34] i.e., in the state of sin and punishment."
  20,102,"the Day when the Trumpet will be blown; on that Day We will gather together the wicked sightless<sup>35</sup> [from horror].","[35] i.e., blind, blue-eyed, blue-faced out of terror."
  20,103,"They will whisper to one another, “You stayed no more than ten days [on earth].”",""
  20,104,"We know best what they will say – the most discerning among them will say, “You stayed no more than a day.”",""
  20,105,"They ask you about the mountains, say, “My Lord will scatter them into dust,",""
  20,106,"and He will leave the earth level and plain,",""
  20,107,"you will not see therein any troughs or peaks.”",""
  20,108,"On that day, they will follow the summoner<sup>36</sup>; none will dare to deviate. All voices will be hushed in awe before the Most Compassionate; you will hear nothing except a whisper<sup>37</sup>.","[36] To the gathering for reckoning. [37] Or the sound of footsteps."
  20,109,"On that day, no intercession will be of any use except to whom the Most Compassionate gave permission and approved his word.",""
  20,110,"He knows all that is ahead of them and all that is behind them<sup>38</sup>, but they do not encompass it<sup>39</sup> with their knowledge.","[38] i.e., what awaits them in the Hereafter and what they did in the world.\n [39] i.e., His knowledge."
  20,111,"All faces will be humbled before the Ever-Living, Self-Sustaining. Those burdened with wrongdoing<sup>40</sup> will be in a total loss.","[40] i.e., sins, evil deeds, or wrongdoing towards others."
  20,112,"But whoever does righteous deeds, being a believer, will have no fear of being wronged or deprived.",""
  20,113,"We have sent it down as an Arabic Qur’an and diversified its warnings, so that they may fear Allah or it may cause them to take heed.",""
